{"tid":498673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油塘劫褻衣猥瑣賊落網","createTime":"2017-12-14T04:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T05:35:52.000Z","uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c5b665b98551f722efa1cb9370e4f19c64e197f","tid":498673,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】油塘劫褻衣怪賊落網，警方憑現場「天眼」鎖定目標，於案發後二十小時在區內拘捕涉案男子，但未尋回女事主被劫去的胸圍及打底褲，正追查贓物去向及賊人犯案動機。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子姓劉（二十四歲），<span style=\"color: red;\">身形矮小，無業</span>，住劫案現場附近一個屋苑，涉行劫罪被通宵扣查，稍後安排進行認人手續。據了解，劉未有涉及風化罪行記錄，平日亦未見異樣，被捕時沒有反抗，警方經搜查其寓所，仍未尋回女事主被劫的失物，包括胸圍及打底內褲，正追查賊人犯案動機及贓物去向。<br />\n<br />\n警方觀塘刑事調查隊在接手調查劫案後，隨即加派人員搜捕，並翻看案發現場油美苑及附近一帶「天眼」片段，終鎖定涉案賊人外貌及行蹤，於是根據逃走路線展開追查，至前晚深夜十一時終掌握疑人所處地點，掩至其居住的屋苑將疑人拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n區內婦女對出現劫褻衣怪賊均人心惶惶，昨知疑匪落網俱感高興。居住案發現場油美苑的姓張女住客稱，事發後一直感到害怕及擔心，前晚更不敢離家，至昨日知悉賊人被捕始放心外出。"},{"pid":"a1eadafd477f63a601815765a31f377821b7865e","tid":498673,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7113dc820d16db2e338032f77034498343e0a92c","tid":498673,"uid":133873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"又要準備定lan線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f42e177f9f044ab79e1b570a29a0275f482d37c","tid":498673,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"居住案發現場油美苑的姓張女住客稱，事發後一直感到害怕及擔心，前晚更不敢離家，至昨日知悉賊人被捕始放心外出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d455220459de36d228d04d62f7876b9e76f20453","tid":498673,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"一定係連登仔"},{"pid":"c3e28312b81c50b8274a64e7fd619da0a5626942","tid":498673,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:19:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要準備定lan線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剛剛訓醒<br />\n講開又講 lan線單野不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364dcdb092c849b41aefd76ef579377c2fe4353d","tid":498673,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>居住案發現場油美苑的姓張女住客稱，事發後一直感到害怕及擔心，前晚更不敢離家，至昨日知悉賊人被捕始放心外出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔出奇既"}]}